Ranger Help for: improvise
==========================

SYNTAX:      improvise
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     110
SKILL TYPE:  attack

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to use the surrounding environment as a
weapon, improvising a terrain-based attack against their current combat
opponent. The type and damage of the attack varies depending on the
terrain: hurling rocks in mountains, using vines in jungle, kicking
sand in desert, and so on. The Ranger must be in active combat to use
this skill. Improvise is powerful but costly, best used when other
options are exhausted.
